00:19:44.118 --> 00:19:45.202
C'est Danny ?

332
00:19:45.660 --> 00:19:46.785
Attends.

333
00:19:47.118 --> 00:19:48.285
Réponds.

334
00:19:48.827 --> 00:19:50.327
Danny, quoi de neuf ?

